ope of Supply</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>4</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Commercial offer</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>5</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Terms &amp; conditions</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Introduction</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>Dear Sir,</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><u>&#160;</u></p>\n<p><u>SUB: Investment Proposal for Application Development to Manage Asset Service &amp; Audit</u></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Thank you very much for your interest in Application Development to Manage Asset Service &amp; Audit. Based on our discussions, we are pleased to offer you our most competitive price proposal for Application Development to Manage Asset Service &amp; Audit.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Please let us know if you need any further clarifications. We will truly remain thankful if you offer us your valuable business opportunity.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>For any further clarifications feel free to contact me on +91 98417 29084 or mail me at <a href=\"mailto:rk@zercorp.com\">rk@zercorp.com</a></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>With regards</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Rajkumar Perumal</strong></p>\n<p>Mobile : +91 98417 29084</p>\n<p>E-mail&#160; : <a href=\"mailto:rk@zercorp.com\">rk@zercorp.com</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.zercorp.com\">www.zercorp.com</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>About Us</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Zercorp is a leading Software development company provides end to end Digital Transformation Solutions. We develop strategic software solutions for businesses across the Globe.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Our Vision</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Our Vision is to be a Preferred Partner for Startup to Enterprise on their Digital Transformation Journey and to be an end to end Digital Transformation Solution provider to Global Customers.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Our Mission</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Our Mission is to make our Customers win their Customer by using our digital platform. We make our customers happy by creating world class products and services. We will produce high quality products and services that is affordable and flexible to our customers.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Our Team</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Suresh Kumar</strong></p>\n<p>Chief Executive Officer | <a href=\"mailto:sk@zercorp.com\">sk@zercorp.com</a></p>\n<p><strong>Kannan</strong></p>\n<p>Chief Technical Officer | <a href=\"mailto:kannan@zercorp.com\">kannan@zercorp.com</a></p>\n<p><strong>Rajkumar Perumal</strong></p>\n<p>Chief Business Officer | <a href=\"mailto:rk@zercorp.com\">rk@zercorp.com</a></p>\n<p><strong>Selvaraj</strong></p>\n<p>Chief Operating Officer | <a href=\"mailto:sr@zercorp.com\">sr@zercorp.com</a></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Scope of Supply</strong></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Modules</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>The proposal aims to develop application to manage asset service &amp; audit for Naga mills. The proposal considers below modules,</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Asset Service with Vendor AMC Module</li>\n<li>Audit with Training &amp; CAPA Module</li>\n<li>Marketing Module</li>\n<li>FG Discard Module</li>\n<li>New Product Development Module</li>\n<li>Outlet and Prospects Visit &amp; Creation Module</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Deliverables</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Detailed Requirements Study before the start of Implementation of the System. As part of this exercise, the Requirements Specification document will be signed by the customer.</li>\n<li>Design, Develop, Test, Build and Install the Application</li>\n<li>Support to Configure the Masters.</li>\n<li>Access to Online/Offline training.</li>\n<li>Training the End Users as per their roles.</li>\n<li>User Acceptance Testing support.</li>\n<li>Setting up of production support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Support Services</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Zercorp attends the troubleshooting and escalation using a customer service system via Mobile / email / remote support (Timing 9.30 AM to 7 PM)</li>\n<li>Operational assistance and technical clarifications six days a week. - Diagnosing problems, resolving simple operational issues.</li>\n<li>Technical clarifications and online support six days a week.</li>\n<li>Onsite Support (Case to case)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>NAGA Responsibility</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A single point of contact (NAGA project coordinator) has to be assigned as a coordinator, to interact with ZERCORP for all system related supports and issues. The coordinator is responsible for conducting additional training for the staff after the sign-off.</li>\n<li>The coordinator will schedule periodic meetings with the managers and staff and facilitate the sign off process. To sign off the Software Requirement Specifications (SRS) document for Customization at the end of Analysis phase.</li>\n<li>Provide all the relevant information for the software to ZERCORP personnel.</li>\n<li>Individual user departments are responsible for the creation of master data and validation of such data to their standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Note: Detailed SOW will be provided after the requirement gathering.<br></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Module Functionalities</strong></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Asset Service with Vendor AMC Module</p>\n<p>Users can create, cancel or update their service tickets based on their role. Once the ticket is created it will be bifurcated to IT or Non-IT. IT tickets are handled by IT team and Non &#8211; IT tickets are handled by maintenance supervisor. Based on the ticketing issue vendors will be selected and checked for their AMC and parts covered under AMC. Supervisor will assign a vendor to solve the issue. If required PO will be generated for vendor.&#160; Once the issue is solved the notification will be sent to required teams and the ticket will be closed.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Ticketing Process Flowchart</strong></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Audit with Training &amp; CAPA Module</p>\n<p>Audit Users will login to the system to get the assigned store to audit by the manager. They will make the Audit plan for week/ month and they visit the store as per the schedule. Assets will be inspected and user will submit the audit points in the system to manager. Manager can validate the audit and he/she has the option to approve or reject the audit. If approved the audit will be closed and sent for report generation. If rejected user has to re-audit as per the instruction and submit the same again. Store user can see the audit report and based on the audit feedback they can take the corrective &amp; preventive action to increase their audit points if required. Admin can add training videos / PDF/ whitepaper in the system and it will be accessible to the Store users to learn more about maintaining the assets.</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Audit Service Flowchart</strong></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Customer Feedback Module</p>\n<p>Outlet users will contact the customers to get their feedback on the system. If the customer ratings are above 4 the system will post the feedback on the record and if it is less than 4 it will be escalated to manager for corrective actions.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>Marketing Module</p>\n<p>This module is sub-divided in to Performance Management System ( PMS), Calendar, Announcement and Intranet for Local collaboration.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Calendar</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>This module gives you the complete overview of the schemes running in the stores, individual travel plan, promotions etc in the calendar / card view format.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Performance Management System ( PMS)</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>System will allow the sales executives to generate the schemes based on their store location to promote the products and they can also work out the cost to run this scheme and also they can provide the projected sales outcome from this scheme. Marketing manager can approve this scheme to run, once it is approved it will be displayed to all user accounts as running scheme for the store. System will pull the actual costing, sales information from wondersoft sales module to co relate with the projected revenue and budgeted scheme.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>Announcement ( PMS)</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>System will pull the information from HRMS pro/ SAP / and from the master data to send the announcements to all the user accounts like their birthdays, service anniversary. They can also the schemes running in their outlet and also other outlets. Best performed outlet can be highlighted in the announcement area and also Top achievers in their respective areas also be highlighted here. And also users can read HR policy using this area.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Intranet</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>System will enable all the users to create a group based on the activity/ department or common. And they can chat using this system to others. This system will enable users to collaborate easily to make things faster &amp; easier.</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>FG Discard Module</p>\n<p>Outlet users can create a discard request based on their available expired, spoiled / contaminated products. Once the request in created the system will enable Area Manager to physically visit and cross check the discard request to confirm the same. RM will re check and find out the source of spoilage and cross verify the documents and send the same to QA team for inspection. QA team will inspect the stock and find out the root cause of the problem and work out the corrective measures of it. Finally GM will verify and approve the Discard .</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>New Product Development Module</p>\n<p>System allow the R &amp; D Head to set timeline for R &amp; D Analysis and Trial process to develop a new product line. Chef will work on the trial process and update the time line and finalise the BOM, shape, taste, spec, size of the product. All employee are allowed to check the product and they can give their valued feedback using this portal. R &amp; D Head review the feedback &amp; time line and send the request to management for new product approval. Before getting in to actual product, outlets can test the products and get the market feedback. Based on the feedback, R&amp; D Head, Chef, Store Team &amp; accounts team can work on the Brand and other statutory packing and costing. And Finally R &amp; D Head / Chef will approve the new product for production.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>Outlet and Prospects Visit &amp; Creation Module</p>\n<p>Sales Executives can find the potential prospects from their outlet based on the geo tagged information and they will feed their data like no. of schools/ colleges/ organization in to the system. They also punch for attendance and travel plan based on the geo tagging. Sales Executives can collect the competitive information and holiday details also in this system.</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Commercial offer</strong></p>\n<p>We are pleased to offer our commercials for you as below:</p>\n<p>&#160;</p>\n<tab